    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Return</strong> the chicken and any resting juices to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bring</strong> to the boil over a high heat and then lower to a gentle simmer</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> a lid and simmer for 10-20 min or until the rice is tender and the chicken cooked through, checking occasionally to prevent sticking</p>",
